## UPLOAD TO GITHUB

```bash
cd ~/ninurta_bank
nano index.html          # Paste FILE 1
nano LICENSE.html        # Paste FILE 2
nano README.md           # Paste FILE 3
git add index.html LICENSE.html README.md
git commit -m "Add complete front-end with security, license, and interactive ATM"
git push origin main
